kpi.name: M1002C517

kpi_info.title: UL DCH SELECTED FOR INTERACTIVE DUE TO BTS HW LIMIT
kpi_info.use: The number of times when E-DCH uplink transport channel cannot be selected in this cell for an interactive class connection because BTS has reported to have no capacity available for E-DCH. When E-DCH cannot be selected as uplink transport channel in this cell because BTS has reported with RADIO RESOURCE MEASUREMENT REPORT to be in state where there is no capacity available for E-DCH.

kpi.kpi_alias: UL DCH SELECTED FOR INTERACTIVE DUE TO BTS HW LIMIT
